-[Jeremiah] Oh my God, no!
No, not the chicken!

00:42.793 --> 00:45.295
-[Sarah] [laughing] It's fake!

00:45.379 --> 00:47.506
-[Jeremiah] That's right,
you eat your dinner, young lady!

00:47.589 --> 00:48.507
You eat your dinner!

00:48.590 --> 00:49.883
[screams]

00:49.967 --> 00:52.469
Ahh, she stabbed me with a chicken!

00:52.553 --> 00:54.888
She stabbed me with a chicken!

00:54.972 --> 00:56.974
[screaming]

00:59.142 --> 01:01.395
[groaning]

01:05.649 --> 01:06.900
[grunts]
-[Sarah] [laughs]

01:06.984 --> 01:09.069
[laughing] Oh, my God,

01:09.152 --> 01:10.487
-You're gonna eat your dinner, sweet girl--

01:10.571 --> 01:11.780
-[Sarah] You got it all over my dress!

01:11.863 --> 01:14.449
-Whether you like it or not.

01:14.825 --> 01:16.493
-[laughs]

01:16.577 --> 01:17.744
-[Jeremiah] It looked pretty real, didn't it?

01:17.828 --> 01:19.121
-Where'd you get this thing?

01:19.204 --> 01:22.874
-[Jeremiah] It's just a
goddamn Thanksgiving decoration.

01:22.958 --> 01:25.752
[both panting]

01:27.170 --> 01:28.880
-Daddy!

01:28.964 --> 01:31.592
-[Jeremiah] [coughs]

01:31.842 --> 01:33.844
-[Sarah] I'm never gonna get this out!

01:56.617 --> 01:59.244
-[Sarah VO] For all my life, I missed my lover.

02:00.662 --> 02:02.664
I wanted my lover.

02:03.248 --> 02:05.208
I wanted to be near my lover.

02:05.292 --> 02:08.170
[dog growls]

02:08.253 --> 02:10.756
But the way my lover
opened and closed my legs...

02:10.839 --> 02:12.341
[dog growls]

02:12.424 --> 02:16.803
The way my lover folded
and unfolded me into my lover's breast,

02:16.887 --> 02:20.057
my lover knows how to love me.

02:20.891 --> 02:22.643
[dog barking]

02:22.726 --> 02:27.731
<i>♪ ambient strings ♪</i>

02:34.905 --> 02:37.449
But things kept getting
in the way of my lover.

02:38.742 --> 02:40.661
And I could not be with my lover.

02:42.287 --> 02:43.705
Until now.

02:44.956 --> 02:48.460
<i>♪♪♪</i>

03:00.097 --> 03:05.102
<i>♪hip-hop playing on radiol'♪</i>

03:20.325 --> 03:25.330
<i>♪ eerie stringe♪</i>

03:55.360 --> 04:00.365
[dogs barking]

04:23.346 --> 04:28.351
<i>♪ Sarah humming softly ♪</i>

04:29.561 --> 04:31.688
-[Jeremiah] What do you
do in your free time, Akin?

04:31.772 --> 04:32.773
Hm?

04:32.856 --> 04:35.776
When you're not throwing
shingles off of rooves.

04:39.446 --> 04:40.989
-I make beer.

04:43.158 --> 04:44.618
-What?

04:47.788 --> 04:49.831
You don't talk much, do you, boy?

04:50.999 --> 04:52.417
-Sorry, sir.

04:52.876 --> 04:54.836
-[Jeremiah] Don't apologize.

04:56.588 --> 05:00.008
<i>♪ humming continues♪'</i>

05:03.678 --> 05:04.638
-Can I take your plate?
-Now, now, son.

05:04.721 --> 05:06.973
No, that's Sarah's job. Let her do that.

05:11.019 --> 05:13.063
[sweeping]

05:22.239 --> 05:23.323
-[Drew on phone] Hey, babe.

05:23.406 --> 05:26.618
I'm just calling because, um...

05:28.411 --> 05:30.080
I had this dream.

05:32.707 --> 05:37.546
It was our wedding day and...
Daddy gave me away to you and...

05:39.047 --> 05:41.216
and when you lifted the veil...

05:43.552 --> 05:47.013
your face just...went away.

05:48.849 --> 05:52.853
You were just, like, a black hole or...

05:53.562 --> 05:56.439
And I woke up with this
feeling in my stomach.

06:02.487 --> 06:04.030
I just wish you would come home.

06:04.114 --> 06:05.782
[alarm beeps]

06:17.961 --> 06:20.297
[fly buzzing]

06:22.883 --> 06:27.888
