10:52.360 --> 10:55.864
-It's just there's something
about the way you carry yourself.

10:55.947 --> 10:58.032
You know, about the way you walk.

10:59.784 --> 11:02.829
It's just you carry a lot
of tension in your shoulders.

11:04.414 --> 11:06.833
Like you got a secret
you don't want anyone to know.

11:08.042 --> 11:09.794
Or maybe you're gay.

11:12.005 --> 11:14.549
-Do you want some more peas?
-[Akin] No, thank you.

11:16.176 --> 11:18.845
-It's not a typical gay walk but, uh...

11:20.013 --> 11:22.682
yeah, there's something
gay about it all the same.

11:29.397 --> 11:31.482
Give Sarah your plate if you're done.

11:47.415 --> 11:52.420
[grunting and laughing]

12:05.016 --> 12:08.811
[heavy breathing]

12:36.256 --> 12:38.633
-[Jeremiah] Sarah, we got another sulker, huh?

12:38.716 --> 12:41.803
It's like we hire one every summer.
Sulkers.

13:20.675 --> 13:24.220
-[Sarah VO] My lover did not know
I was waiting for my lover.

13:24.304 --> 13:29.309
[indistinct TV sounds]

13:32.895 --> 13:37.108
But I held my lover
like a knife holds its bread.

13:37.191 --> 13:39.360
I could feel-- [echoing]
I could feel through my body

13:39.444 --> 13:42.655
who my lover was
and how to become close to--

13:42.739 --> 13:44.490
[overlapping]
Who my lover was...

13:45.742 --> 13:48.494
and how to become close to my lover.

13:48.578 --> 13:53.583
[crickets chirping]

14:10.391 --> 14:13.019
-[Jeremiah] Do you know
any constellations, Shoulders?

14:18.191 --> 14:19.567
[branch snaps]

14:21.652 --> 14:24.572
[thunder]

14:54.644 --> 14:59.649
[crickets chirping]

15:06.823 --> 15:08.449
-[Sarah] Are you following me?

15:10.952 --> 15:12.245
-No.

15:14.288 --> 15:15.998
-[Sarah] Are you sure?

15:25.425 --> 15:26.968
-[Sighs]

15:41.441 --> 15:46.446
<i>♪ indistinct singing on distant TV.♪</i>

15:52.493 --> 15:54.829
[chainsaw buzzing]

16:00.626 --> 16:03.796
[hammering]

16:03.880 --> 16:04.922
{Akin} [grunts]

16:09.343 --> 16:11.053
-[Jeremiah] You okay, son?

16:12.680 --> 16:13.931
-Yes, sir.

16:19.103 --> 16:24.108
[cows mooing]

16:47.548 --> 16:49.884
-You don't like him, do you, girl?

17:03.356 --> 17:08.361
