19:16.072 --> 19:17.823
-[Drew on phone] [inaudible].

19:17.907 --> 19:19.533
What'd you say?

19:24.664 --> 19:26.207
-[Sighs]

19:26.290 --> 19:28.250
-[Drew on phone] [inaudible].
-Hello?

19:29.335 --> 19:31.671
-[Drew on phone]
Hey, [inaudible].

19:31.754 --> 19:33.464
-[Akin] Nothing's wrong.

19:34.340 --> 19:36.342
[softly] I shouldn't have come.

19:38.135 --> 19:41.472
-[Drew on phone] [inaudible].

19:42.348 --> 19:44.517
-[Akin] [voice cracking]
I know we need the money.

19:46.102 --> 19:48.396
-[Drew on phone] [inaudible] I miss her.

19:48.479 --> 19:50.523
-[Akin] [whispering] I miss her too.

19:53.067 --> 19:58.072
[breathing heavily]

20:14.296 --> 20:19.301
[rustling]

21:03.095 --> 21:04.764
-[Sarah] Jeremiah!

21:07.391 --> 21:08.976
Daddy!

21:12.146 --> 21:13.814
Jeremiah!

21:15.149 --> 21:17.151
-[Jeremiah] Yeah.
-[Sarah] The cows got out.

21:17.234 --> 21:18.778
I can't find Flowers.

21:18.861 --> 21:21.489
-[Jeremiah] Ugh, well,
saddle up and go look for her,

21:21.572 --> 21:23.157
all right?
-[Sarah] Okay.

21:23.240 --> 21:25.743
-[Jeremiah] Like a coyote when she roams.
Shoulders!

21:25.826 --> 21:27.161
Come here.

21:27.787 --> 21:29.288
Come here!

21:29.371 --> 21:31.290
I want you to show him
the property line, all right?

21:31.373 --> 21:33.292
Where that fence needs a fix.

21:35.044 --> 21:36.796
-[Sarah] Okay.

21:38.255 --> 21:39.632
Come on.

21:42.384 --> 21:46.305
[breathing heavily]

21:46.388 --> 21:50.351
<i>I soft ambient strings ♪</i>

21:50.434 --> 21:52.144
[horse grunting]

21:52.228 --> 21:54.063
Whoa, come on.

21:58.442 --> 21:59.777
[dog barks]

22:04.657 --> 22:08.035
You've got a long life ahead
if you work cattle and you don't ride horses.

22:12.248 --> 22:14.291
-[Akin] I just don't get
along with them real well.

22:17.253 --> 22:18.796
-[Sarah] One kick you?

22:18.879 --> 22:20.005
{Akin} Hm?

22:20.089 --> 22:22.299
-[Sarah] Did you get kicked
when you were young?

22:23.634 --> 22:25.052
-[Akin] Yeah, maybe.

22:26.220 --> 22:27.555
-[Sarah] Well...

22:27.638 --> 22:29.849
did you or didn't you?

22:32.643 --> 22:34.353
-[Akin] No, I didn't get kicked.

22:34.436 --> 22:35.729
[clicks tongue]

22:39.233 --> 22:40.609
-[Sarah] Knock knock.

22:42.111 --> 22:43.028
-[Akin] Who's there?

22:43.112 --> 22:44.029
-[Sarah] Boo.

22:44.113 --> 22:47.449
-[Akin] Boo who?
-[Sarah] [laughs]

22:54.456 --> 22:56.041
Hi, Flowers!

22:58.252 --> 23:00.087
-[Akin] [whispering] Come here.

23:00.713 --> 23:02.464
