23:05.301 --> 23:06.886
Oh, my God!

23:07.511 --> 23:09.096
I just saw one.

23:10.681 --> 23:13.100
Did you ever catch frogs
when you were little, Akin?

23:13.893 --> 23:15.394
-[Akin] ♪-

23:15.477 --> 23:17.104
-Really?

23:18.522 --> 23:20.357
-[Akin] I don't like amphibians.

23:21.692 --> 23:23.569
-Really? I love them.

23:26.113 --> 23:27.323
Ahh!

23:31.619 --> 23:32.703
Oh!

23:32.786 --> 23:34.705
-[Akin] I don't like anything that slithers.

23:34.788 --> 23:37.124
-[Sarah] I do. [laughs]

23:49.345 --> 23:52.181
He almost went in my shirt. [laughs]

23:56.310 --> 23:57.937
[laughs]

24:03.025 --> 24:04.443
[laughs]

24:04.526 --> 24:06.278
That feels so funny.

24:06.362 --> 24:07.780
[laughs]

24:09.198 --> 24:10.616
[laughs]

24:32.262 --> 24:33.555
Whoa.

24:36.850 --> 24:38.352
Bad frog.

24:44.066 --> 24:45.567
[laughs]

24:47.569 --> 24:48.988
[grunts]

25:07.256 --> 25:10.175
[both moaning]

25:25.399 --> 25:27.276
[moaning] Oh, God.

25:30.320 --> 25:33.365
[heavy breathing and moaning]

25:33.449 --> 25:34.450
No.

25:35.034 --> 25:36.326
[groans] No!

25:36.410 --> 25:38.370
Ah!
-[Akin] Shh.

25:38.454 --> 25:43.208
[heavy breathing and grunting]

25:44.501 --> 25:46.211
[flies buzzing]

25:48.338 --> 25:53.302
[both grunting and moaning]

26:06.315 --> 26:11.320
[both breathing heavily]

26:32.174 --> 26:35.594
[river running]

26:35.677 --> 26:40.682
[cow mooing frantically]

26:49.942 --> 26:54.488
[heavy breathing]

26:54.571 --> 26:56.949
[cow mooing]

27:11.672 --> 27:13.090
-[Sarah] Come on, Flowers. Get!

27:13.173 --> 27:14.633
Go! Go, go, go!

27:18.554 --> 27:22.516
[breathing heavily]

27:29.731 --> 27:31.066
[sighs]

27:40.242 --> 27:41.869
-[Jeremiah] You like to cook, Akin?

27:41.952 --> 27:44.663
A man should know
how to cook green beans.

27:44.746 --> 27:46.248
You know how to cook green beans?

27:48.625 --> 27:50.711
-[Akin] I mostly just cook simple things.

27:51.670 --> 27:53.547
-[Jeremiah] Simple things like eggs?

27:53.630 --> 27:55.966
A man should know how to cook eggs.

27:56.049 --> 27:57.551
