28:10.606 --> 28:11.857
Is that true?

28:13.400 --> 28:15.444
-[Akin] I mean, I've never been to one.

28:17.779 --> 28:20.532
-How do you...do your wash?

28:21.700 --> 28:23.744
-[Akin] Well, we have a washing machine.

28:28.290 --> 28:30.334
-Who's "we?"

28:30.417 --> 28:32.377
-[Akin] Me and my roommate.

28:32.461 --> 28:33.545
-[Jeremiah] Hm.

28:33.629 --> 28:35.881
