29:05.285 --> 29:07.871
I mean, that's the way
I've had issues with buzzards.

29:12.668 --> 29:14.169
You know...

29:15.671 --> 29:19.758
it doesn't bother me, son,
if somebody lies to me.

29:28.850 --> 29:31.770
You got a tan line around your finger, son.

29:32.729 --> 29:34.773
