29:37.651 --> 29:39.444
Hoping to get a little action this summer?

29:39.528 --> 29:40.862
-No, sir.
-[Jeremiah] Yeah.

29:40.946 --> 29:44.283
Yeah, and if you are,
you're more than welcome to it.

29:48.954 --> 29:51.164
Oh, and by the way,
thank you for doing that milking.

29:52.082 --> 29:54.751
That's gonna be your regular job now, all right?

29:59.172 --> 30:00.674
-[Akin] Yes, sir.

30:06.596 --> 30:09.683
[fly buzzing]

30:10.600 --> 30:11.977
[sighs]

30:20.527 --> 30:25.532
[crickets chirping]

30:28.118 --> 30:29.536
Hey!

30:30.704 --> 30:32.122
Hey.

30:35.959 --> 30:37.336
That's my job.

30:38.170 --> 30:39.546
-I know.

30:40.339 --> 30:41.923
-[Akin] Why are you doing my job?

30:42.966 --> 30:44.843
-Uh, well, I like to.

30:44.926 --> 30:47.137
You can do another job.

30:51.767 --> 30:53.560
Hey, your wife's real pretty.

30:55.645 --> 30:57.314
-What?

30:57.397 --> 30:59.691
-[Sarah] And you already have a baby.
You lied about that.

31:01.943 --> 31:03.862
-[Akin] Where'd you get that?

31:03.945 --> 31:05.530
-[Sarah] Your door was unlocked.

31:05.614 --> 31:07.074
