31:09.034 --> 31:10.994
-[Sarah] Your personal what?

31:12.788 --> 31:15.082
-Look, please don't go in my room again.

31:16.666 --> 31:18.460
-[Sarah] I can't promise that, Akin.

31:19.669 --> 31:20.879
-[Akin] Why not?

31:22.923 --> 31:24.257
-[Sarah] Well...

31:25.342 --> 31:26.802
-Why not?

31:28.804 --> 31:29.721
-[Sarah] Let's go.

31:29.805 --> 31:30.722
[goat bleats]

31:30.806 --> 31:32.182
Yes.

31:32.265 --> 31:33.642
[goat bleats]

